pageContext.claim: “And I have to tell you, they [China] bought the largest amount of corn and soybeans that they've ever bought -- that anybody's -- I think they said it was a record of soybean and record of corn and that's a tremendous thing.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump routinely claims that China recently placed the largest order of soybeans in history. But no orders by China in 2020 have made it in the list of the top 15 daily sales.
